reviewText: Love this collection... and great low price... awesome find!!!

I really family movies the most these days they are fun and most often things come out right, Grown up movies can often invite one into a world that is much more dangerous, unhappy, complicated than most people's why go there I have worked tohelp a section of that group in difficult worlds for years, watching a movie about it doesn't help them.

I wanted to buy these because i wanted to watch them again for old times sake. I used to love My Magic Dog so much! I would bug my parents to let me rent it every time we would go to the store when i was a kid. The movies seem corny now, yet kind of cute in a way.
